# Language

The entire text of this document has to be written in UK English.


# Figures

All figures are to be produced directly using tikz. Figures using includegraphics{} to include raster graphics directly is not allowed, and likewise for PDFs. These figures scale badly with respect to typography consistency.


# LaTeX warnings

All warnings producing during LaTeX build are taken to be serious. Committed source files shall not produce warnings in this regard.
